## Comparison

| Option | Pros | Cons | Best For |
|--------|------|------|----------|
| **Console + Agent** | Agent handles batching, retries | Requires agent setup | ECS Fargate, Docker |
| **Winston CloudWatch** | Direct integration, no agent | Uses Winston only | All deployments |
| **Pino AWS** | Lightweight | Fewer features | Performance-critical |
| **Custom Transport** | Full control | More code | Specific requirements |

---

